{"tid":1798074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"襪子裏藏生物樣本回國， 中國男準備搭乘海航航班時在機場被攔截","createTime":"2019-12-26T03:16:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T06:25:30.000Z","uid":313615,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"b100795369508db61c766db2e7a6851b30856f83","tid":1798074,"uid":313615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T03:16:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.washingtonexaminer.com/news/hidden-in-a-sock-chinese-researcher-accused-of-trying-to-smuggle-vials-of-biological-material-out-of-us\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonexaminer.com%2Fnews%2Fhidden-in-a-sock-chinese-researcher-accused-of-trying-to-smuggle-vials-of-biological-material-out-of-us&d=xSG8yb8yy9PjQoJ4RYEJZHwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=df224a01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.washingtonexaminer.com/news/hidden-in-a-sock-chinese-researcher-accused-of-trying-to-smuggle-vials-of-biological-material-out-of-us</a><br />\n<br />\n中國研究人員鄭鑿松（Zaosong Zheng，音譯）12月9日在波士頓的一個國際機場準備搭機返回北京時被捕。海關在鄭的行李箱中的襪子內發現了21小瓶棕色液體。鄭涉嫌竊取美國實驗室的生物樣本。<br />\n<br />\n綜合波士頓新聞網站&ldquo;Universal Hub&rdquo;和《華盛頓觀察家報》等媒體報導，29歲的鄭鑿松是位於廣州的中山大學的一名博士生，研究重點在膀胱癌和腎癌。他在美國貝斯以色列醫院（Beth Israel Hospital）以一名病理學訪問學生身份做了一段時間的研究工作。12月9日，鄭在波士頓洛根國際機場（Logan International Airport）準備搭機回中國時被拉。"},{"pid":"7cff24e5b480865bbea6440e391b2f6de9fee016","tid":1798074,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T03:16:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">和你貼 連儂廁</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1796473\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1796473</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3ed300a369208d2390905c1e482e4ad546ce5508","tid":1798074,"uid":313615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T03:18:21.000Z","msg":"21管咁係將整篇paper嘅試劑都備好。<br />\n<br />\n都幾敬業嘅，諗住實實在在噉做paper<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d236d3c7a576f6f4627fb862fa6d822cd29085","tid":1798074